Welcome.
\n<Rui>...Who are you?

\n<Guide>I am a guide. Lady Rui, you will be descending
into this world shortly.
\n<Rui>...Descend into a world?

\n<Guide>A different world from here. A very ordinary world
where people live their daily lives, accumulating
days.
\n<Rui>...Like a god. Who are you?

\n<Guide>I am a guide. A powerless being whose only role is
to guide Lady Rui.

\n<Guide>The person you will be replacing is a guild
member. She is a mercenary woman in this world who
hunts monsters and earns her daily bread.

\n<Guide>She cannot use magic and fights with dual swords,
dancing through battle just like you, Rui-san.

\n<Guide>Like her, you, Rui-san, will also be unable to use
magic once you switch places.

\n<Rui>So I'm going to that world as a substitute for
that woman... It's like role-playing.

\n<Guide>And the task she has taken on this time is the
"extermination of a goblin den."

\n<Guide>It's not a job for a woman to take on alone.
However, you have accepted this request due to the
provocation of your fellow mercenaries.

\n<Guide>By now, the guild is probably buzzing with bets on
how many goblins you will give birth to.
\n<Rui>...That's a terrible story.
\n<Guide>Now, the world is drawing near.

\n<Guide>Once again, the clear condition for this door is
\C[1]【to collapse the goblin den】\C[0].
\n<Rui>...You're telling me to commit a massacre?

\n<Guide>Massacre. That's slightly off. What we ask of you
is extermination.

\n<Guide>The goblins of this world are beasts that cannot
understand humans.

\n<Guide>Individually weak, but they are vile beings whose
principle of action is to ensnare humans.

\n<Guide>Especially young women suffer terribly. To
goblins, human women are the most suitable
livestock for breeding.
\n<Rui>...

\n<Guide>Therefore, they instinctively target human women
relentlessly.

\n<Guide>And once they capture a woman, they continue to
impregnate her until death, and finally kill and
consume her in a gruesome manner.
\n<Guide>They are truly the enemies of mankind.

\n<Guide>Having heard this story, do you still have your
conscience?
\n<Rui>...I can't let that stand.

\n<Guide>That's good to hear. Good intentions are far too
powerless against pure malice.

\n<Rui>...Alright. It seems like it will be for the good
of the people in that world, so I'll clear it
quickly for them.
\n<Guide>It seems you are ready.
\n<Guide>Then, have a good journey.
this.ClearPtcAll();
